Interpretation: Set lock_at to null for Assignment ID 220 in course 778 (removing the lock date so submissions remain accepted after previous lock time).
Risk assessment: Modifying — changes submission window and may allow late submissions indefinitely; reversible by setting a new lock date.
Preview: Archives Project (ID 220)
• Current lock_at: 2026-10-30T23:59:00Z
• New lock_at: null (no automatic closing)
• Unlock and due_at unchanged
Proposed action (will not run until you confirm):
